Mark a lens as last-used. Subsequent `/me` reads return it as `last_requested_lens`, so all composite tools default to it.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} after the user explicitly switched contexts (e.g. created a new lens via leadbay_create_lens).

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} in normal flow — leadbay_pull_leads and leadbay_adjust_audience auto-set the right lens.

{{include:headers/verification-required-if-write}}
